      "heading": "求耶和華退敵"
    },
    {
      "type": "desc",
      "contents": []
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 1,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "From my earliest youth my enemies have persecuted me. Let all Israel repeat this: "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
